Meet <b>Quanasia</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>This friendly girl lives comfortably at <a href='/home/?user=chantaljr915'>80756 Park Avenue</a> in Metro Park. Since January 3, 2006, she has built a reputation for having one of the most enviable homes in town. Currently a duplex, the home boasts plenty of couches, eye-catching color combos, and a totally stocked trophy case! <br><br>Quanasia's teachers have always admired her for being observant. She is considerate of all those around her and listens to and absorbs what her peers say. This gives her a great advantage when it comes to acting, one of her favorite hobbies, because she has a great sense of how people behave. She also uses her skills in English class when analyzing books. She can pick up on subtle metaphors and parallels that lead to a richer interpretation of the story.<br><br>When she's not stocking up on clothes and furniture in her favorite colors (red, violet, and pink), she enjoys working on her singing voice in the shower. She belts out her favorite R&B, rap and pop tunes and it gets her totally energized!     <br><br>Thanks for being a good citizen, Quanasia, and congratulations on being Millsberry's Citizen of the Week!</div>
